::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe growls as the shot barely misses his head, grazing his shoulder. 
This bot was going to die a slow death....

He speeds up, gaining on the bot he was chasing. His mouth opens, showing the 
horrid collection of teeth of different species, ready to bite down on his 
victim as soon as he caugh up to it.
